title: Best Memories for Folk & Pop Lovers (Dutch Treat ^C062 HQ)
description:
Same as for C061, you missed it? Received as a gift, I can only pass it through because the list deserves to be shared with all. Its a well balanced playlist with quite a few oldies whit a lot of impact. Sound is not as good as C061 (oldies!) but whatever..... Enjoy,
